  "narrative": "<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Short impact summary</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">Economic Diversification in Nigeria (2022), published by Bloomsbury Publishing Plc.. Scholarly uptake (strength 0.6). 19 citations \u2014 measurable academic uptake.</p>\n<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Full narrative</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">Economic Diversification in Nigeria was published by Bloomsbury Publishing Plc. in 2022. Conceptually, the work connects to Diversification (marketing strategy), Subsistence agriculture, Curse, Agriculture and Politics.</p>\n<p class=\"story-text\">OpenAlex records 19 citations. Citations peaked in 2025 with 8 citing works. Notable citing venues include SSRN Electronic Journal, Africa\u2019s global engagement and African Journal of Environmental Sciences and Renewable Energy. Inferred role: Scholarly uptake. 1 formal book review(s) in the citation record.</p>\n<p class=\"story-text\">4139 recorded downloads via open-access infrastructure.</p>",
